🚀 Step 1: Access the Game
Option A: Play Online (Recommended)
Go to your GitHub repository: https://github.com/bonusbazarshop-cmd/Ateeb-Fight
Click the file index.html
Click "Raw" button
Or enable GitHub Pages in repo settings and access the live link
Option B: Play Locally
Clone the repository:
bash
git clone https://github.com/bonusbazarshop-cmd/Ateeb-Fight.git
cd Ateeb-Fight
Open index.html directly in your browser (just double-click the file)
🎯 Step 2: Main Menu
When you start the game, you'll see three options:

Code
🎮 ATEEB FIGHT 🎮
├─ 👾 Single Player (Play 5 levels vs AI)
├─ 👥 2-Player VS (Local battle with friend)
└─ 🏆 Leaderboard (View top scores)
🕹️ Step 3: Game Controls
Single Player Mode
Action	Key
Move Up	W
Move Down	S
Move Left	A
Move Right	D
Shoot	Space
Use Power-up	E
Pause	ESC
2-Player Mode
Action	Player 1	Player 2
Move	W A S D	↑ ← ↓ →
Shoot	Space	Enter
Power-up	E	P
🎮 Step 4: Gameplay
Your Character 🔵
Player 1: Electric Blue circle with eyes
Player 2: Hot Pink circle with eyes
Has 100 HP (Health Points)
Auto-aims at nearest enemy
Enemies 👾
Lime Green Aliens - Chase you
Orange Robots - Strafe and dodge
Show health bars above them
Drop powerups when defeated
Your Goal
Defeat all enemies in each wave
Complete 3 waves per level
Survive and stay healthy (HP > 0)
Progress through 5 levels
📊 Step 5: 5 Levels Progression
Level	Name	Enemies	Difficulty	Challenge
1	🏋️ Training Ground	5-8 slow aliens	⭐ Easy	Learn controls
2	🤖 Robot Factory	8-12 robots	⭐⭐ Medium	Faster enemies
3	👽 Alien City	12-18 mixed	⭐⭐⭐ Hard	Very fast
4	🛸 Space Station	15-20 mixed	⭐⭐⭐⭐ Extreme	Intense battle
5	💥 Boss Battle	1 Boss + waves	⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Insane	Ultimate challenge
⚡ Step 6: Power-ups (Collect & Use)
When you defeat enemies, they drop power-ups:

Power-up	Icon	Effect	Duration
Speed Boost	⚡ Yellow	2x faster movement	5 seconds
Rapid Fire	🔫 Orange	3x fire rate	5 seconds
Shield	🛡️ Blue	Absorbs 1 hit	Until hit
Health	❤️ Red	+30 HP	Instant
Bomb	💣 Purple	Clears all enemies	Instant
🎯 Step 7: Scoring System
Code
Total Score = (Enemies Killed × 100) + (Time Bonus × 10) + (Combo Bonus)

Combo Multiplier:
- Kill 3+ enemies quickly → 2x multiplier
- Kill more = higher multiplier (up to 3x)
- Displayed as "COMBO x2!" on screen
📈 Step 8: HUD (Head-Up Display)
Top Bar shows:

📍 Current Level
💯 Current Score
🎯 Combo Multiplier (if active)
👾 Enemy Count
Bottom Bar shows:

❤️ Health Bar
🌊 Wave Progress (e.g., "Wave 2/3")
💀 Kill Count
⏱️ Time Remaining
🏆 Step 9: Win/Lose Conditions
You Win When:
✅ Defeat all enemies in all 3 waves ✅ Health > 0 ✅ Level completes ✅ Advance to next level!

You Lose When:
❌ Health drops to 0 ❌ Time runs out ❌ Get hit too many times ❌ Game Over screen appears

💾 Step 10: Save Your Score
When you complete a level or game over:

Enter your name in the text box
Click "Submit Score"
Score is saved to localStorage (persistent)
Check Leaderboard to see top 10 scores
